name: Kuda Izuna | 久田イズナ (Blue Archive)
description:
The cutest ninja in Kivotos!

(16/06/2023) - LoRA got nuked once because of the swimsuit + gym samples. Great stuff.

Samples tested at 1 strength on Anything v4.5.

Use these trigger words to get Izuna's characteristics:

  • 1girl, izuna, short hair, fox ears, halo

Some outfits that she can use:

School Uniform:

  • serafuku, sailor collar, sleeveless, skirt, scarf, floral print, fishnets, single thighhigh, hair ornament, partially fingerless gloves

Swimsuit:

  • striped bikini, visor cap, denim shorts, scarf, hair flower

Gym Uniform (might not work properly since not enough dataset):

  • white gym shirt, pink buruma, puffy sleeves, short sleeves, hair ornament

Have fun!
